Package com.qoretechnologies.qorus.workflow

Class WorkflowDataHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.qore.jni.QoreObjectWrapper
      • com.qoretechnologies.qorus.workflow.WorkflowDataHelper
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DynamicDataHelper, StepDataHelper, TempDataHelper
    public class WorkflowDataHelper
extends org.qore.jni.QoreObjectWrapper
    Java wrapper for the OMQ::UserApi::Workflow::WorkflowDataHelper "WorkflowDataHelper" class in Qorus This class is a helper class that allows dynamicdata "workflow dynamic data" (DynamicDataHelper) and tempdata "workflow temp data" (TempDataHelper) to be read and updated atomically; the write lock for the data is grabbed in the constructor and released in the destructor. The %Qore-language destructor is run at the end of the Java step execution, after the step returns to Qorus.
